# {{ project_name }}

Production Multi-Agent Supervisor template generated by `create-agent-app`.

## Overview

This template uses a supervisor-worker architecture:
- Supervisor decides which worker to run next.
- Researcher worker gathers information via web search.
- Writer worker synthesizes researcher output into final answer.

## Graph Flow

```text
START -> supervisor_node
supervisor_node -> researcher_node
supervisor_node -> writer_node
supervisor_node -> END (FINISH or iteration limit)
researcher_node -> supervisor_node
writer_node -> supervisor_node
```

## Setup

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\\Scripts\\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env
python main.py
```

## API

```bash
uvicorn api.main:app --reload --port 8000
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/query -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"query":"Research and summarize AI memory architectures"}'
```
